1
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:15,280
Don't be scared, come play with me

2
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:24,920
I'm right here

3
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,960
Mr. Zheng, you are hard to invite

4
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:54,120
Today you came to gather bones for our Zhao Family

5
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,360
You've truly gone to a lot of trouble

6
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,880
I'm only doing a job for pay

7
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,000
Well...

8
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,120
Help! Bin'er!

9
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,760
Put out the fire, quick, brother

10
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:19,200
Put it out, quick! Help!

11
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:23,560
Help! Help!

12
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,880
Bin'er

13
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,200
Bin'er

14
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:36,520
Bin'er! Brother!

15
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,800
How is the Zhao Family doing?

16
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,160
Brother Xunan's passing

17
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,920
hit her very hard

18
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,440
I must help her uncover the truth

19
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,640
So you really are devoted to your sister-in-law

20
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,840
Who could it be?

21
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,440
Li Zhong harmed young girls

22
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,200
Burning him alive was what he deserved

23
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,120
He got what he deserved

24
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:11,120
Could there have been more to Li Zhong's case?

25
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,480
I leave it to you two

26
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,840
Thank you for your hard work, both of you

27
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,640
Today, no matter what, use every possible means

28
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,760
you must calm Li Zhong's wronged spirit

29
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,640
Do not let him come out and stir up trouble

30
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:29,640
and restore peace to the people of Nanwan Town

31
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,240
Thank you, thank you

32
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,960
You are too polite, Mayor

33
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,960
Rest assured, Mayor

34
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,640
Leave it all to me

35
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:39,280
I trust Master Jiang to handle it

36
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,480
Mysterious Ancestor of Heaven and Earth

37
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,120
Root of all vital forces

38
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:52,400
Cultivated through countless ages

39
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,360
Bear witness to my power. Pick more carefully

40
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,600
There

41
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,520
There seems to be another piece, there

42
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,040
Can you hurry up?

43
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,040
You are interfering with my ritual here

44
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:19,360
Not one step of the bone-gathering ritual can be skipped

45
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:21,280
This is respect for the dead

46
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,480
He was only a villain

47
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,360
Aren't you just a fraud too?

48
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,320
You... say that again

49
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,000
All right, all right

50
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:35,880
You two are both doing this for Nanwan Town's people

51
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,880
Whatever it is, can't it be discussed calmly?

52
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,040
Take it easy, talk it out

53
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,160
Calm down, calm down

54
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,080
Master, look at this

55
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,640
Master, all this was prepared for you

56
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:51,120
Tomorrow at noon, I will formally perform the ritual

57
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,720
Thank you for your trouble, Master, thank you

58
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:03,360
Waiter

59
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,200
Bring me a bowl of noodles

60
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,680
Right away, sir

61
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:09,240
So it's Mr. Zheng. What a coincidence

62
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,960
You are...?

63
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,280
Master Jiang's disciple

64
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,880
Just call me Xiao Shen

65
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:19,560
Waiter, put this table on my tab

66
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,960
Right away, sir

67
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,360
Consider this meal my treat

68
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,480
Let me apologize to you

69
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,200
My master just has that kind of temper

70
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,760
Please do not take offense

71
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:32,960
This disciple is much more reasonable than his master

72
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,120
Even if everyone says Li Zhong was an evil man

73
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,960
only you, Mr. Zheng, gave him the same respect

74
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,120
With virtue like yours

75
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,360
I truly admire you

76
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,640
My master once said

77
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,120
as a Bone Collector

78
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,280
no matter what the dead did in life

79
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,840
all must be treated equally

80
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,920
Whether one wielded great power in life

81
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,360
or lived an ordinary life

82
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:02,840
after death, all become a skeleton

83
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,400
Well said

84
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:09,080
I have learned from your words

85
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,880
Good heavens

86
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,800
Now I am going to make a fortune

87
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:37,480
Why does Master Jiang always talk nonsense?

88
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:41,720
You'd better not say it again.

89
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:44,520
Come with me, quickly.

90
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,400
Master, I bought the wine.

91
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,680
Master, what's wrong?

92
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,560
There's a ghost!

93
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,560
There's a ghost!

94
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,240
Master!

95
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,800
There's a ghost!

96
00:06:59,360 --> 00:06:59,840
A ghost!

97
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,360
There's a ghost!

98
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,760
There's a ghost!

99
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:11,800
Master Jiang, where are you rushing off to?

100
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,240
The curse is here.

101
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,520
The curse has really come.

102
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,120
Ghost!

103
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,240
Run, quick!

104
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:31,920
Help!

105
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,560
Help!

106
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,640
Help!
